==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sumless
<hw>Sum"less</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not to be summed up
or computed; so great that the amount can not be ascertained;
incalculable; inestimable.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Sumless treasure.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Pope.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Summarily</ent>⟦br⟧
